STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Juan GUERRERO-ESTRADA, a/k/a Juan C. Estrada, Juan C. Guerrero, Juan Carlos Guerrero, Juan C. Guerrero-Estrada, Juan C. GuerreoEstrada, Defendant-Petitioner. State of New Jersey, Plaintiff,
v.
Juan M. Flores Santos, a/k/a Juan M. Flores-Santos, Defendant. C-712 September Term 2017
080359 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 19, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-2375/2821-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
